天，外媒爆料OpenAI正进军好莱坞，与电影制片人、导演建立合作关系。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="160" data-backw="562" data-height="454" data-imgfileid="504976053" data-ratio="0.2851851851851852" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1590" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb15vkIiaOXDekALZUeOc71rwnyu4I5cW66wwxjBibQtqKD3EjXR8ZCxuK8wFlQ92UuA1bD64PQJLTicg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">而此前，就连好莱坞大导Tyler Perry直言，自己在看完Sora制作的视频后，直接搁置了自己影视工作室8亿美元的扩建计划！</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">现在，除了电影制作领域，音乐行业也即将被AI攻陷了。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-height="1074" data-imgfileid="504976056" data-ratio="0.9944444444444445" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1080" style="width: 171px;height: 170px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb15vkIiaOXDekALZUeOc71rwaHK2f1HQ4TalwzD2IqIr8GnZ9bu79M5YRwlpTu6OUXA4qHO4qO7cPw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><div autoid="1895" data-style-type="0" style="max-width: 100%;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;"><div style="padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-co